description: PIER 4 in Boston's Seaport emerges as a serene waterfront community, surrounded by water on three sides, providing a living experience unlike anywhere else. This exceptional premiere corner residence has a thoughtfully designed open-concept layout encompassing 3BR and 2.5BA. The gourmet kitchen features Gaggenau appliances, gas cooktop, white marble countertops, a spacious pantry, and a wine fridge. Step onto the private balcony, creating the sensation of living directly on the water. Enjoy the convenience of two full garage spaces (side by side) and guest parking for residents' visitors. This boutique-style building offers a suite of amenities including a fully equipped gym, golf simulator, dog spa, owners lounge, grill, fire pit and 24-hour concierge and doorman. Seaport's upscale dining, nightlife, and world-class shopping are mere steps away.
